---
// Process component showing our methodology
---

<section id="process" class="process">
  <div class="section-container">
    <h2>Our Process</h2>
    <p class="section-description">We follow a proven methodology to ensure successful outcomes for every project.</p>
    
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="icon-placeholder">1</div>
        <h3>Discovery</h3>
        <p>We begin by understanding your vision, goals, and the challenges you face.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="icon-placeholder">2</div>
        <h3>Strategy</h3>
        <p>We develop a comprehensive plan that aligns with your objectives and timeline.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="icon-placeholder">3</div>
        <h3>Execution</h3>
        <p>We implement the strategy with precision, keeping you informed every step of the way.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step">
        <div class="icon-placeholder">4</div>
        <h3>Results</h3>
        <p>We measure success and ensure your goals are achieved, then plan for future growth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process {
    background-color: white;
  }

  .process h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .process-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .step {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .icon-placeholder {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: var(--accent-blue);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .step p {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .process h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .section-description {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .process-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .step {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .icon-placeholder {
      width: 45px;
      height: 45px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .step h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
